snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | RE MANN | Shreya Ghoshal x Swanand Kirkire x Kanishk Seth
snippet.description:
Do you remember what it felt like? The first time you stepped onto campus? Butterflies in your  stomach as you eagerly awaited the world before you. From the joy of personalizing your own nook in the dorm to chatting away with newly made friends in the canteen, these memories will forever remain. 
 
#ReMann will take you on a nostalgic journey through time, while also gently holding the hands of those who are setting out on it for the very first time. Sharing perhaps what they hoped to have known then, India’s most celebrated artists, Shreya Ghoshal and Swanand Kirkire and Kanishk Seth bring to all of us, a warm hug, when it's needed the most. Khayalon se na darr, kal ki chod de fikar!
 
🎶 Listen to Re Mann now On - https://umgindia.lnk.to/REMann

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Bayo | Cyli Khare x Srushti Tawade x Komorebi
snippet.description:
Celebrating the beauty and strength of Maharashtrian culture, through its women. 
Maratha culture rests proudly on the shoulders of its graceful and empowered women. She’s a force of nature, a fistful of sand, an elusive dream.
Bayo is for all women to come together for themselves. To embrace your confidence, your dreams and your voice. The force of all women stands tall with you. Bayo is a beautiful reminder to invoke your inner strength and the strength of your tribe. 

Led by the lyrical powerhouse and singer Cyli Khare, along with Maharashtra’s home-grown rapper Srutsti Tawde, Bayo’s verses are fierce and thought-provoking. The eclectic and unconventional Komorebi adds her electronic touch to the telling sounds of Maharashtra and is joined by fellow producer Curtain Blue to stitch together a sonic tale of empowerment.
Coke Studio Bharat proudly presents Bayo- for the women of today.
